## ğŸ§ª **Example Snippet: Training an MLP Classifier**

```python
net = MLPClassifier(
    hidden_layer_sizes=(256, 64, 15, 3),
    activation="logistic",
    random_state=1,
    max_iter=500
).fit(X_trainscaled, y_train)

print("Accuracy:", net.score(X_testscaled, y_test))
```

---

## ğŸ“ˆ **GridSearchCV Example**

```python
clf = GridSearchCV(
    MLPClassifier(random_state=1),
    param_grid=tuned_parameters,
    cv=3,
    n_jobs=-1,
    verbose=5
)
clf.fit(X_trainscaled, y_train)
```

